To install:

 - symlink the directory to ~/.vim
 - symlink the vimrc file within this directory to ~/.vimrc
 - run the script setup.sh, which will set up the submodules
   and command-t.

To update the submodules yourself:

 - git submodule foreach git pull origin master

You can learn more about managing your .vim files using git 
by reading this article: 

- http://vimcasts.org/episodes/synchronizing-plugins-with-git-submodules-and-pathogen/